Package: polyglot
Version: 0.6.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Your Name <your.email@example.com>
Description: Universal compiler and interpreter wrapper
 Polyglot is a universal compiler and interpreter wrapper that detects
 programming languages by file extension and executes them with the
 appropriate toolchain.
 .
 Features:
  - Supports 30+ programming languages
  - Automatic language detection
  - Auto-install missing toolchains
  - Watch mode for development
  - Colored output
  - Comprehensive configuration
Homepage: https://github.com/yourusername/polyglot
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31)
Recommends: python3, nodejs, ruby, php, perl, lua5.3, gcc, g++
